<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Things I Share (Posts by dg-pb)</title><link>https://dg-pb.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://dg-pb.github.io/authors/dg-pb.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><copyright>Contents © 2025 &lt;a href="mailto:digpob@gmail.com"&gt;dg-pb&lt;/a&gt; </copyright><lastBuildDate>Sun, 05 Oct 2025 09:12:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>Python's try-finally</title><link>https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/</link><dc:creator>dg-pb</dc:creator><description>&lt;p&gt;So there is an ongoing process regarding disallowing / forbidding return/break/continue that exit a finally block.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="reference external" href="https://peps.python.org/pep-0765/"&gt;See the most recent accepted PEP regarding this&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And the last new update regarding this is that issuing a warning might be problematic and there might be the case that either:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol class="arabic simple"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;That sort of usage needs to be deprecated, or&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;warning needs to be rolled back and let linters handle it.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is rather meant to explain how current mechanics work in as simple as possible manner.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;So in short, things are not as complicated or even tricky as the impression that I got by reading a PEP and discourse conversations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And, in my opinion, the issue is not that it is complicated, but rather the fact that some nuances are almost never needed, thus forgotten or never understood in the first place.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are only 2 rules:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="code"&gt;&lt;table class="codetable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-1"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number=" 1"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-1" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class="c1"&gt;# @lambda f: print(f())  # 2&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-2"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number=" 2"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-2" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class="k"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nf"&gt;finally1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;():&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-3"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number=" 3"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-3" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-3"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;     &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;"""&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-4"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number=" 4"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-4" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-4"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;     NOTE:Rule No.1:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-5"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number=" 5"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-5" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-5"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;         The return value of a function is&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-6"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number=" 6"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-6" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-6"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;             determined by the last return&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-7"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number=" 7"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-7" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-7"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;             statement executed.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-8"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number=" 8"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-8" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-8"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;         Since the finally clause always&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-9"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number=" 9"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-9" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-9"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;             executes, a return statement&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-10"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="10"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-10" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-10"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;             executed in the finally clause&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-11"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="11"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-11" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-11"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;             will always be the last one&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-12"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="12"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-12" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-12"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;             executed.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-13"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="13"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-13" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-13"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;     """&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-14"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="14"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-14" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-14"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;     &lt;span class="k"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-15"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="15"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-15" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-15"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;         &lt;span class="k"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-16"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="16"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-16" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-16"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;     &lt;span class="k"&gt;finally&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-17"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="17"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-17" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-17"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;         &lt;span class="k"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-18"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="18"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-18" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-18"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-19"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="19"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-19" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-19"&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class="c1"&gt;# @lambda f: print(f())   # 6 (no error)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-20"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="20"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-20" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-20"&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;span class="k"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nf"&gt;finally2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;():&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-21"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="21"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-21" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-21"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;     &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;"""&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-22"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="22"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-22" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-22"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;     NOTE:Rule No.2:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-23"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="23"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-23" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-23"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;         If the finally clause executes&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-24"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="24"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-24" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-24"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;             a return, break or continue&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-25"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="25"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-25" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-25"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;             statement, that jumps out&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-26"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="26"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-26" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-26"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;             of the finally clause, the&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-27"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="27"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-27" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-27"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;             saved exception is discarded.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-28"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="28"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-28" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-28"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="sd"&gt;     """&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-29"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="29"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-29" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-29"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;     &lt;span class="k"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="ow"&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nb"&gt;range&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;10&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;):&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos linenodiv"&gt;&lt;a href="https://dg-pb.github.io/posts/pythons-try-finally/#rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-30"&gt;&lt;code data-line-number="30"&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;a id="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-30" name="rest_code_3243d302ffb34510a7f963225f5178d5-30"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;         &lt;span class="k"&gt;try&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
